VIRTUALISATION

software used for virtualisation is Hyperwiser
ex clould computing take use of virtual machines.

There are two types of virtualisation
1. TYPE 1 
2. TYPE 2

In type 1 virtualisation :
when memory is allocated to hyperwiser , the total memory occupied by the software could  be more than the initial memory.

in type 2 virtualisation:
type 2 runs on the host OS to provide virtualisation management and other services.
